# Kodaelus (project stub)

For use in **any** project without copying this repo, run once from the Kodaelus distribution folder:

```bash
npm run install:global
```

That installs `~/.cursor/agents/kodaelus.md` and `~/.cursor/kodaelus/instructions.md`. Select **kodaelus** from the agent menu in any workspace.

When developing this repo only, you may also read `kodaelus/instructions.md` here.
